Package oracle.kubernetes.operator.logging

Class MessageKeys

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.kubernetes.operator.logging.MessageKeys
  • public class MessageKeys
extends Object
    Message keys used to look up log messages from the resource bundle. The use of message keys makes the code more readable.
